        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "It seems to me that the assemble function in Zend_Controller_Router_Route could use a little adjustment to equalize its behaviour to the match function when using translated segments.\n\nAssemble uses Zend_Controller_Router_Route->getLocale() to determine the current locale (if no @locale is given in the data array).\n\n{code:title=Zend_Controller_Router_Route->assemble}\n    public function assemble($data = array(), $reset = false, $encode = false, $partial = false)\n    {\n        if ($this->_isTranslated) {\n            $translator = $this->getTranslator();\n            \n            if (isset($data['@locale'])) {\n                $locale = $data['@locale'];\n                unset($data['@locale']);\n            } else {\n                $locale = $this->getLocale();\n            }\n        }\n\t\t...\n{code}\n\nThe match function does a direct query to Zend_Translate_Adapter->getMessages() which results in Zend_Translate_Adapter->_options['locale'] being used as current locale.\n\n{code:title=Zend_Controller_Router_Route->match}\n    public function match($path, $partial = false)\n    {\n        if ($this->_isTranslated) {\n            $translateMessages = $this->getTranslator()->getMessages();\n        }\n\t\t...\n{code}\n\n{code:title=Zend_Translate_Adapter->getMessages}\n    public function getMessages($locale = null)\n    {\n        if ($locale === 'all') {\n            return $this->_translate;\n        }\n\n        if ((empty($locale) === true) or ($this->isAvailable($locale) === false)) {\n            $locale = $this->_options['locale'];\n        }\n\n        return $this->_translate[(string) $locale];\n    }\n{code}\n\nSo in some cases one could end up with match and assemble using different locales.\nShouldn't match better look something like this:\n\n{code:title=Zend_Controller_Router_Route->match (revised)}\n    public function match($path, $partial = false)\n    {\n        if ($this->_isTranslated) {\n            $locale = $this->getLocale();\n            $translateMessages = $this->getTranslator()->getMessages($locale);\n        }\n\t\t...\n{code}"
        },
